{"tid":334931,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"其實內地黎嘅小朋友都幾好呀，大家做乜咁憎佢地？","createTime":"2017-07-25T07:41:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-25T08:03:39.000Z","uid":18656,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c589fda728f3bcc51a96bd5c04119d47a3918666","tid":334931,"uid":18656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T07:41:14.000Z","msg":"啱啱搭火車係沙田落，咁我就起身落車啦，但係太多人所以我都等左陣，之後有件蝗死肥仔夾硬衝入黎之後仲要一直用蝗語話「我的位置！我的位置！」仲要撞翻落車嘅人入去。之後我忍夠啦，咁啱手上有個裝滿嘢嘅A4紙箱，於是就將佢夾左係塊玻璃同扶手中間，之後佢個位冇左就係度喊，真係好撚爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢老母仲要係出面入唔到車廂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd238cbe2d319fcdf92792685bb247b90bb37e16","tid":334931,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T07:46:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d9325c536a09e7d2ae209d5c4579bafba15b7335","tid":334931,"uid":18656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T07:48:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大蝦細，俾屎餵呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蝦埋啲大嘅就唔同講法<br />\n繼續努力</blockquote><br />\n個大嘅我都唔小心批咗佢一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"096817efc129814f5b707c9bcc7d1fb13796d9d5","tid":334931,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T07:51:17.000Z","msg":"所以你冇落到車，大家雙輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a33d6a2c16b2cd233adb89a044151c76c833e7f6","tid":334931,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T07:51:18.000Z","msg":"樓主比人炒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2af28a0d3bf36a46c25a696cd74c1442afacaae","tid":334931,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T07:51:24.000Z","msg":"惻隱之心 人皆有之<br />\n對住蝗童想傷害一下佢地係好正常 好正確嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\